  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p1', 'Support our ministry today—your generosity helps us spread the Gospel, serve families, and impact lives for Christ.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p2', 'At Yeshua Deliverance Ministries (YDM), our mission is to reach souls, build families, and impact communities with the love and power of Jesus Christ. Every donation you make is more than just a contribution—it is a seed of faith that fuels the growth and expansion of our ministries.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p3', 'Your generosity enables us to spread the Gospel, nurture believers in their walk with Christ, and create opportunities for transformation both locally and globally. By supporting YDM, you partner with us in teaching, serving, equipping leaders, strengthening families, and extending compassion to those in need.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p4', 'Whether given once or as a monthly commitment, your gift has eternal impact. Together, we can continue to build a strong foundation of faith that will bless generations to come.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p5', '🙏 Thank you for standing with YDM and helping us advance the Kingdom of God.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p6', 'Your generosity directly supports the growth and impact of Yeshua Deliverance Ministries (YDM) in meaningful ways, such as:', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p7', 'Every time you give to YDM, you’re helping fulfill the mission to reach people for Christ.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p8', 'At YDM, Your generosity makes a difference! Every gift helps us spread hope, serve our community, and share God’s love with those in need. Thank you for being a part of this mission!', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'body.p9', 'Your gift helps Yeshua Deliverance Ministries build a Creator’s Studio, equipping us with the tools to share God’s word worldwide through podcasts, videos, and digital media.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.supportydm', 'cta.1.href', 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fydministries.ca%2Fcampaigns%2Fsupportydm%2F', 'url'),
