  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p1', 'Your donation isn’t just a financial contribution; it’s a commitment to nurturing a community where education thrives, and healthcare is accessible to all.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p2', 'Yeshua Deliverance Ministries is launching aTech Fundraiserto build our Creator’s Studio—a dedicated space where we will produce podcasts, YouTube videos, worship messages, and other digital content to share the gospel with excellence.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p3', 'Currently we are operating on outdated equipment that no longer performs at it’s full intended potential. We would love to update our tech space with the necessary equipment needed to serve you better.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p4', 'This studio will give us the tools to reach far beyond our physical walls, creating an online presence that inspires, teaches, and empowers people worldwide. Every gift helps us purchase the equipment and resources needed to bring this vision to life.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p5', 'Together, we can spread God’s word further and stronger through the power of media.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p6', 'Your generous support will go directly toward:', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p7', 'Every time you give to YDM, you’re helping fulfill the mission to reach people for Christ.', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p8', 'At YDM, Your generosity makes a difference! Every gift helps us spread hope, serve our community, and share God’s love with those in need. Thank you for being a part of this mission!', 'richtext'),
  ('campaign.techfund', 'body.p9', 'Your gift helps Yeshua Deliverance Ministries build a Creator’s Studio, equipping us with the tools to share God’s word worldwide through podcasts, videos, and digital media.', 'richtext'),
