  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'body.p1', 'Bishop Huel O. Wilson is a devoted servant of God with a lifelong commitment to preaching, teaching, and shepherding God’s people.', 'richtext'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'body.p2', 'From his early years in faith to his decades of ministry, he has remained steadfast in his calling to share the Gospel, encourage families, and guide believers in their spiritual journey. Known for his dynamic preaching and compassionate leadership, Bishop Wilson continues to inspire and uplift those he serves with wisdom, humility, and love.', 'richtext'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'body.p3', 'Beyond his ministry, he enjoys the simple joys of life as a family man and follower of Christ—reading the Word, spending time with his loved ones, cooking, gardening, and strengthening bonds through fellowship. His life is a testimony of faith in action, showing that true leadership flows from a heart devoted to God, service to others, and a desire to see lives transformed for the Kingdom of Christ.', 'richtext'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'hero.title', 'Bishop Huel O. Wilson', 'text'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'meta.description', '', 'text'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'meta.title', 'Bishop Huel O. Wilson', 'text'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'sections.h3_1', 'Short Biography', 'text'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'sections.h3_2', 'Education & Experience', 'text'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'sections.h3_3', 'Working Shifts', 'text'),
  ('profile.bishopwilson', 'sections.h3_4', 'My Articles', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'body.p1', 'She packed her seven versalia, put her initial into the belt and made herself on the way. When she reached the first hills of the Italic Mountains, she had a last view back on the skyline of her hometown Bookmarksgrove, the headline of Alphabet Village and the subline of her own road, the Line Lane.', 'richtext'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'body.p2', 'Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts. Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean. A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth. Even the all-powerful Pointing has no control about the blind texts it is an almost unorthographic life One day however a small line of blind text by the name of Lorem Ipsum decided to leave for the far World of Grammar. The Big Oxmox advised her not to do so, because there were thousands of bad Commas, wild Question Marks and devious Semikoli, but the Little Blind Text didn’t listen.', 'richtext'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'hero.title', 'Clementina Wilson', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'meta.description', '', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'meta.title', 'Clementina Wilson', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'sections.h3_1', 'Short Biography', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'sections.h3_2', 'Education & Experience', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'sections.h3_3', 'Working Shifts', 'text'),
  ('profile.clementinawilson', 'sections.h3_4', 'My Articles', 'text'),
