  ('sermon.discovering_the_power_of_waiting', 'sections.h3_1', 'Is it a Good Thing, or a God Thing?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.discovering_the_power_of_waiting', 'sections.h3_2', 'We  are Asking for that Help Today', 'text'),
  ('sermon.discovering_the_power_of_waiting', 'sections.h3_3', 'God Loves Us', 'text'),
  ('sermon.discovering_the_power_of_waiting', 'sections.h3_4', 'Trust in Him', 'text'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p1', 'So we do not lose heart. Though our outer self is wasting away, our inner self is being renewed day by day.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p2', 'Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary. The languages only differ in their grammar, their pronunciation and their most common words. Everyone realizes why a new common language would be desirable: one could refuse to pay expensive translators. Their separate existence is a myth.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p3', 'To achieve this, it would be necessary to have uniform grammar, pronunciation and more common words. If several languages coalesce, the grammar of the resulting language is more simple and regular than that of the individual.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p4', 'The languages only differ in their grammar, their pronunciation and their most common words. Everyone realizes why a new common language would be desirable: one could refuse to pay expensive translators. Their separate existence is a myth.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p5', 'To achieve this, it would be necessary to have uniform grammar, pronunciation and more common words. If several languages coalesce, the grammar of the resulting language is more simple and regular than that of the individual.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p6', 'It’s a great pleasure reading your post!', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'body.p7', 'Thanks.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.do_not_lose_heart_your_future_in_christ_is_beyond_all_comparison', 'cta.1.href', 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fydministries.ca%2Fhow-to-develop-a-habit-of-worship%2F', 'url'),
