  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p1', 'It was never God’s intent that we who were created in His image would experience slavery, oppression or evil of any kind.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p10', 'It’s a great pleasure reading your post!', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p11', 'Happy to be of service.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p12', 'Thanks for sharing this information is useful for us.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p13', 'Always happy to be of service.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p14', 'This is awesome!!!', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p15', 'Thanks.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p16', 'Happy to be of service.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p2', 'We are committed to providing our patients with the highest quality of care.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p3', 'To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is.The European languagesare members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary. The languages only differ in their grammar, their pronunciation and their most common words.Everyone realizeswhy a new common language would be desirable: one could refuse to pay expensive translators. To achieve this, it would be necessary. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is. The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p4', 'The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary. The languages only differ in their grammar, their pronunciation and their most common words. Everyone realizes why a new common language would be desirable.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p5', 'The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages. It will be as simple as Occidental; in fact, it will be Occidental. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is. The European languages are members.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p6', 'To an English person, it will seem like simplified English. Their separate existence is a myth. The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages. It will be as simple as Occidental; in fact, it will be Occidental. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is. The European languages are members of the same family.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p7', 'The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages. It will be as simple as Occidental; in fact, it will be Occidental. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is. The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p8', 'Their separate existence is a myth. The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages. It will be as simple as Occidental; in fact, it will be Occidental. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is. The European languages are members of the same family.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.experiencing_the_freedom_of_gods_presence', 'body.p9', 'The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary. The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport.', 'richtext'),
