  ('sermon.how_do_i_intercede_for_family_who_dont_believe_in_jesus', 'hero.title', 'How Do I Intercede For Family Who Don’t Believe In Jesus?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_do_i_intercede_for_family_who_dont_believe_in_jesus', 'meta.description', '', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_do_i_intercede_for_family_who_dont_believe_in_jesus', 'meta.title', 'How Do I Intercede For Family Who Don’t Believe In Jesus?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_do_i_intercede_for_family_who_dont_believe_in_jesus', 'sections.h3_1', 'Fuel Your Faith and Don’t Give Up', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_do_i_intercede_for_family_who_dont_believe_in_jesus', 'sections.h3_2', 'Create a Prayer Battle Plan', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_do_i_intercede_for_family_who_dont_believe_in_jesus', 'sections.h3_3', 'Anabaptist or Puritan?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'body.p1', 'We often talk about developing a daily habit of prayer and reading God’s Word. But what about worship? How do we practically incorporate worship into our busy schedules and develop a habit of worship?', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'body.p2', 'Some practical knowledge that I have learned through experience, and my walk with Jesus, is simple. God is a God of peace, not a God of confusion.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'body.p3', 'A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy, my dear friend.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'body.p4', 'I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence, that I neglect my talents. I should be incapable of drawing a single stroke at the present moment; and yet I feel that I never was a greater artist than now.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'body.p5', 'Wow, cool post, thanks for sharing.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'body.p6', 'Happy to be of service.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'cta.1.href', 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fydministries.ca%2Fhow-to-develop-a-habit-of-worship%2F', 'url'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'cta.1.label', '', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'cta.2.href', 'https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fydministries.ca%2Fhow-to-develop-a-habit-of-worship%2F&text=We%20often%20talk%20about%20developing%20a%20daily%20habit%20of%20prayer%20and%20reading%20God’s%20Word.%20But%20what%20about%20worship?%20How%20do%20we%20practically%20incorporate%20worship%20into%20our%20busy%20schedules%20and%20develop%20a%20habit%20of%20worship?', 'url'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'cta.2.label', '', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'cta.3.href', 'https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fydministries.ca%2Fhow-to-develop-a-habit-of-worship%2F&title=How%20to%20Develop%20a%20Habit%20of%20Worship&summary=We%20often%20talk%20about%20developing%20a%20daily%20habit%20of%20prayer%20and%20reading%20God’s%20Word.%20But%20what%20about%20worship?%20How%20do%20we%20practically%20incorporate%20worship%20into%20our%20busy%20schedules%20and%20develop%20a%20habit%20of%20worship?&source=https%3A%2F%2Fydministries.ca%2Fhow-to-develop-a-habit-of-worship%2F', 'url')
