  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'meta.title', 'How to Develop a Habit of Worship', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'sections.h3_1', 'Explore New Opportunities', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'sections.h3_2', 'Where Does Our Help Come From', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'sections.h3_3', 'So, Where are We Asking for That Help Today?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'sections.h3_4', 'Do You Pray for Your Sin?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.how_to_develop_a_habit_of_worship', 'sections.h3_5', 'What’s Your View of Marriage?', 'text'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p1', 'I know that I for one have done things in my life that I certainly regret. I think all of us have. As a pastor, I’ve heard many people’s stories about how personal sin ruined their relationships and livelihoods. It’s heartbreaking to witness the collateral damage of sin.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p2', 'We are committed to providing our patients with the highest quality of care.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p3', 'The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary. The languages only differ in their grammar, their pronunciation and their most common words. Everyone realizes why a new common language would be desirable: one could refuse to pay expensive translators. The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p4', 'I know that I for one have done things in my life that I certainly regret. I think all of us have. As a pastor, I’ve heard many people’s stories about how personal sin ruined their relationships and livelihoods.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p5', 'Please complete all questions. Mark the best answer from the choices given.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p6', 'Good Blog!', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.i_ruined_my_lifeis_there_hope_for_me', 'body.p7', 'Thanks.', 'richtext'),
