  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p1', 'Growing up, I was not enamoured with the thought of my own wedding day. For some odd reasons, I wasn’t consumed looking at wedding magazines nor dreamt about the venue or gown I should have at my future wedding.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p2', 'We are committed to providing our patients with the highest quality of care.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p3', 'The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages. It will be as simple as Occidental; in fact, it will be Occidental. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p4', 'The new common language will be more simple and regular than the existing European languages. It will be as simple as Occidental; in fact, it will be Occidental. To an English person, it will seem like simplified English, as a skeptical Cambridge friend of mine told me what Occidental is. The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary. The languages only differ in their grammar, their pronunciation and their most common words. Everyone realizes why a new common language would be desirable: one could refuse to pay expensive translators. To achieve this, it would be necessary to have uniform grammar, pronunciation and more common words. The European languages are members of the same.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p5', 'Please complete all questions. Mark the best answer from the choices given.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p6', 'Wow, cool post, thanks for sharing.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'body.p7', 'Thanks for sharing this information is useful for us.', 'richtext'),
  ('sermon.whats_your_view_of_marriage', 'cta.1.href', 'https://faith-connect.cmsmasters.net/main/author-page/', 'url'),
