  ('sermon.your_mission_should_you_choose_to_accept_it', 'body.p1', 'Most of us know exactly where that line comes from. Beginning with the original TV series in 1966 to the current $4B movie franchise starring Tom Cruise, Mission: Impossible has become almost ubiquitous in our pop culture.', 'richtext'),
