  ('singleton.maltoncog', 'body.p1', 'Our curriculum appeals to student diversity and interest, and is rigorous and challenging. We understand each child comes to us with different talents, learning styles, and identities. And we celebrate that difference because our diversity is our strength.', 'richtext'),
